92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/IMG_3332.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/IMG_3330.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/IMG_3331.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/IMG_3330.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/IMG_3332.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/IMG_3331.jpg"], "content": "<p>We found a box of artist copies of the Minted book wen sorting through inventory and are making them available for MintFace readers to own. </p><p>The artist copies are special because they were handmade in New Zealand in a short run for early supporters. That means each book was bound, stitched and gold foiled by hand. They are truly a book for the art collector including almost 100 artists who minted for the first time in 2021.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/IMG_3329.JPG 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Once these are gone, there are no more first edition artist copies.</p><h3 id=\"minted-book-artist-edition\">Minted Book artist edition</h3><p>0.1 eth ea (including worldwide delivery from NZ)<br /><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x10c4e41be66cf083507cd9ada45fb4f4f70bed89/2\">https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x10c4e41be66cf083507cd9ada45fb4f4f70bed89/2</a></p><p>Once purchased, DM your wallet address and physical address to send to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced\">@mintfaced on Twitter</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/IMG_3333.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/10/IMG_3332.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/IMG_3332.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/IMG_3332.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a